ter for three days straight. The quickest solution for the Protagonists is to use Alien and Paranoia-1 to shut down the Hospital Incident Culprit candidates.\n\nAs a Mastermind, this is a bit annoying, but since I created this with the intent of it being a smooth First Steps script, I consider this a correct solution."
